Commentary Text: Siraj to Saha, out Caught by Parnell!! One handed stunner from Parnell and the crowd go bonkers. Has to be the catch of the match, surely? Saha skipped down the track used his wrists to thump this drive over the infield and for a fleeting moment, he seemed to have timed it well enough to claim a boundary. Parnell, at cover, though leaps up to his fullest and plucks the ball out of thin air with his left hand. Saha c Parnell b Siraj 12(14) [4s-2]
